Package uk.org.mygrid.cagrid.domain.interproscan

Class Summary
Classification Classification the found feature is classified in.
InterProScanInput Represents an input to the Taverna-wrapped InterProScan service that Taverna will convert and actually invoke the service.
InterProScanInputParameters Input parameters for the InterProScan job.
InterProScanJob  
InterProScanOutput This is the output of the Taverna-wrapping of the InterProScan service; contains the protein the InterProScan was run for and a collection of found features for the given protein in various databases in InterPro warehouse.
InterProScanService Represents Taverna-wrapping of the InterProScan service to be deployed on caGrid and used by caGrid clients.
ProteinDomain Represents a record of the protein domain in the database where it was found in.
ProteinDomainIdentifier  
ProteinDomainLocation Represents the location of the found domain in the protein sequence.
ProteinDomainLocationStatistics  
ProteinDomainMatch Represents a found signature in the given protein sequence.
